Available Tools: get_ticket_status | list_open_tickets | add_reply | close_ticket | reopen_ticket
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "ticket_id": "string", "customer_id": "string", "reply": "string" }
Response Schema: { "ticket_id": "string", "status": "open|in_progress|resolved|closed", "replies": [{ "author": "string", "message": "string", "timestamp": "string" }] }
---
Question: Could you verify the current status of ticket T-1129 for customer C-501 to see if the database migration is complete?
